496
00:33:42,854 --> 00:33:45,118
<i>And you think Gran's story is your ticket?</i>

497
00:33:45,189 --> 00:33:46,952
<i>I think it's a story worth telling.</i>

498
00:33:47,025 --> 00:33:48,549
<i>I'd love to have you with us.</i>

499
00:33:48,626 --> 00:33:51,117
- Really?
- Yes. Of course.

500
00:33:51,529 --> 00:33:52,621
We would.

501
00:34:39,777 --> 00:34:42,678
SOPHIE: How much time
did you actually spend with Lorenzo?

