00:34:43,114 --> 00:34:45,014
CLAIRE: Every second that we could.

503
00:34:45,516 --> 00:34:49,850
<i>I'd go to meet him after class,
to the farm where he was working,</i>

504
00:34:49,921 --> 00:34:54,984
<i>and we'd sit under the trees and we'd share
