00:35:08,406 --> 00:35:10,704
and the springs of fresh water,

511
00:35:11,175 --> 00:35:13,803
<i>and we'd walk for miles and miles.</i>

512
00:35:14,145 --> 00:35:16,272
<i>We'd lie in the dry grass.</i>

513
00:35:16,814 --> 00:35:18,611
I can still remember

514
00:35:19,884 --> 00:35:23,718
the smell of his sweet, hot sweat and...

