588
00:40:35,633 --> 00:40:37,157
<i>Impossible.
We're going home in the morning.</i>

589
00:40:37,234 --> 00:40:40,761
Come on, Charlie, will you calm down?
Sophie, what do you think?

590
00:40:40,838 --> 00:40:43,932
<i>Gran, what do you mean,
what does she think? She doesn't think.</i>

591
00:40:44,008 --> 00:40:48,001
<i>This was her brilliant idea. It's over! Done!
We found Nemo.</i>

592
00:40:48,078 --> 00:40:49,636
