00:41:07,631 --> 00:41:11,727
Oh, please, all right. I went to Brown.
Double Major. Minor in Latin.

601
00:41:11,802 --> 00:41:13,736
<i>This is madness. It's madness.</i>

602
00:41:14,305 --> 00:41:18,002
<i>Charlie, didn't you say
