00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:34,412
<i>Ciao. How are you?</i>

617
00:42:35,052 --> 00:42:37,043
<i>I'm good. How are you?</i>

618
00:42:37,121 --> 00:42:39,487
You know what?
I was just witnessing this most incredible,

619
00:42:39,557 --> 00:42:40,990
incredible Sauterne auction.

620
00:42:41,058 --> 00:42:43,424
<i>It was just beautiful. It was incredible.
