00:42:55,773 --> 00:42:56,967
You know what, baby? You know what?

627
00:42:57,041 --> 00:42:59,669
<i>I mean, this isn't a good time because
I'm in the middle of something,</i>

628
00:42:59,743 --> 00:43:02,974
<i>but, I mean, I'm glad you called because
